        <abstract> 
<p>Will send first six chapters [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] for the press. Sends data on size of MS and book. His "beau ideal" for type and size is Lyell’s <hi rend="italic">Manual</hi> [<hi rend="italic">of geology</hi>] 1st ed.</p> 
            <p>Important to his health to get the work printed quickly. Must leave home soon to stay for months at a water-cure establishment.</p>
            <p>Asks printer to send a proof-sheet a day until he gets well ahead.</p>
        </abstract>
